content:
What's different about Friday compared to other days? (thinking)
...{短暂停}
Oh right, there's usually commissions on Fridays.

Today, our Neighbors...{短暂停}
Busy, weary, yet at peace,
As if something is coming to an end.

...{短暂停}
Is it just my imagination?
The neighbors seem quite busy today.

Each day I put it off adds to the pile,
I should be more anxious about this, so...{短暂停}
Time to get back to work.

...(thinking)
Oh, you and the other Neighbors, {短暂停}
you all look so happy today.
